@node "Wymagania" "Wordworth v5 PL - requirements"

Requirements

To run Wordworth v5.0  you need KickStart v2.0 or higher,  hard disk & MC68020
recommended. 

@endnode

@node "Instalacja" "Wordworth v5 PL - installation"

Installation

To install  polish wersion of  Wordworth v5 run  installeráfrom  this archive. 
Enter path, where you have original Wordworth. Next run Wordworth.

